Part.P:
The University Libraries’ website (
library.sbuniv.edu
) is an excellent source for information.  In addition to the University Libraries’ catalog and databases, general information about library hours, policies, collections, archives, course related web resources, branch library information, and a very useful Research Guides are just a few of the resources available on the site. The University Libraries provide access to a significant number of electronic resources, including full-text articles, e-books and databases. These resources are available via the University Libraries’ website, and are accessible on or off campus.
